      <title>监管机构称韩国将提高金融市场吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-make-financial-markets-more-attractive-regulator-says-2024-01-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融监管机构周一表示，韩国将采取措施，使其金融市场对投资者更加友好，对外国人更具吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-make-financial-markets-more-attractive-regulator-says-2024-01-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 05:35:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾谴责中国海警对菲律宾渔民的“挑衅行动”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-condemns-provocative-action-by-chinese-coastguard-against-filipino-2024-01-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家安全委员会发言人周一表示，菲律宾谴责中国海警对菲律宾渔民的最新“挑衅行动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-condemns-provocative-action-by-chinese-coastguard-against-filipino-2024-01-22/</guid>
