    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚普拉博沃在选举民意调查中巩固领先优势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-strengthens-lead-election-polls-2024-01-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名民意调查机构周六表示，随着世界第三大民主国家即将于 2 月 14 日举行选举，印尼总统候选人领跑者普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 在最新的民意调查中扩大了对对手的领先优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-strengthens-lead-election-polls-2024-01-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 11:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本超薄月球飞船成功登月后电力不足</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/japan-starts-precision-landing-moon-sniper-slim-spacecraft-2024-01-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本周六成为第五个将航天器送上月球的国家，但太阳能问题可能会缩短该国证明“精确”着陆技术并重振遭受挫折的太空计划的使命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/japan-starts-precision-landing-moon-sniper-slim-spacecraft-2024-01-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 13:36:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大使馆警告韩国整形手术风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassy-warns-plastic-surgery-risks-south-korea-2024-01-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国驻首尔大使馆警告公民注意在韩国进行整形手术的危险，从死亡风险到导致难以通过移民检查的重大面部变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassy-warns-plastic-surgery-risks-south-korea-2024-01-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 11:19:47 GMT</pubDate>
